Ahmad ibn 'Ali ibn Muhammad ibn Hajar al-'Asqalani ; tahqiq Yusuf 
'Abd al-Rahman al-Mar'ashli. al-Tab'ah 1. [Riyadh] : al-Mamlakah 
al-'Arabiyah al-Sa'udiyah, Wizarat al-Shu'un al-Islamiyah wa-al-
Awqaf wa-al-Da'wah wa-al-Irshad bi-al-ta'awun ma'a al-Jami'ah al-
Islamiyah bi-al-Madinah al-Munawwarah, <1999 > $17.20 (U.S.). v. 
<16, pt. 1-2 > ; 25 cm. (al-Jami'h al-Islamiyah fi al-Madinah al-
Munawwarah, 1) Hadith; texts; authorities; early works to 1800. 
 ISBN : 9960770737
